      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCaf317cb82afb100587be8d91941052d2"></a>Removing the brake discs
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4079"> </a>The front brake discs consist of an inner carrier, which is mounted to the wheel, and an outer rotor. Both parts must be changed
            together as a pair.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4082"> </a>Remove the front wheel (<a href="78597.html#DUCdadae6602ae710058dcd8dcc6a5141d2">Removing the front wheel</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e4087"> </a>Loosen the retaining screws (1) securing the disc to the wheel, remove the disc (2) and, on its left side, slide out the phonic
            wheel (3).
         </div>
      </div>
